Samsung has expressed readiness to partner with other Original Equipment Manufacturers (OEMs) to offer trade-in service for its newly released devices.  Glo said: “Pre-ordering starts from 10 p.m., February 1, 2023, at all Gloworld shops across Nigeria. The offer includes the Eco package which comes with Samsung S-23, Samsung smartwatch5 pro, and a Pre-order gift, while the Only Device package comes with Samsung S-23 and a Pre-order gift.” 